Package Summary
Package
Description
edu.cnm.deepdive.rps
Base package of RPS ecosystem app.
edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.controller
UI controller classes (AppCompatActivity and Fragment subclasses) and any supporting nested classes.
edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.hilt
Dagger/Hilt modules that provide methods to satisfy dependencies which are not completely handled by Inject and other Hilt dependency-injection mechanisms.
edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.model.domain
Domain classes, abstracting and implementing properties and behaviors of objects in the problem domain (specifically, an idealized intransitive ecosystem) of the application.
edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.service
Repository and service classes providing access (at least potentially) to device & external services, preferences, the app's persistent data store, and the domain model.
edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.view
Custom subclasses of View for rendering model state in the UI.
edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.viewmodel
ViewModel and AndroidViewModel subclasses maintaining cross-configuration-change state (and providing high-level asynchronous mutation operations on the app's mutable state, persistent or otherwise) for UI controllers.
